&lt;p&gt;15+ years of experience managing operations for large scale data centers.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;An understanding of AI/ML workloads, including power, cooling, and network connectivity&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
